COLORIZE: Toggle ANSI color output

Syntax: colorize [off]

Enables or disables ANSI color output. Color is off by default.
When color is on, room exits appear in bold green.
Your preference is saved across logins.

Type 'colorize' to turn color on. Type 'colorize off' to turn it off
again.
Or manually: setenv TERM ansi

SEE ALSO: color, terminal
